g\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fuptow%2Fi4%2F976cda76f2555ff04b2b7c1cb4916d87.jpg&h=696ade2c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n阿貢火山上次大規模噴發是在1963年2月至1964年1月，其中2月與3月的主要噴發都各造成上千人的死傷，同時，亦有數萬人無家可歸。<br />\n<br />\n今年8、9月，阿貢火山突然出現活動反應，自當時起已撤離25000多人。"},{"pid":"b30d9ba8ef9971b6c170e5f80033c152147053d4","tid":481468,"uid":5490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T11:23:27.000Z","msg":"快啦"},{"pid":"216d2839b0f326775fc6b536b0b2ebc04410524c","tid":481468,"uid":18692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T12:36:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"181942a4b23f298887aebd5624d4c0e493c6ede9","tid":481468,"uid":98659,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T12:57:58.000Z","msg":"D蝦片一定會炒到貴晒 係時候入貨strong hold"},{"pid":"074cd4478550b8c03174808a99b155529f52a90a","tid":481468,"uid":18772,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T13:08:49.000Z","msg":"唔知近唔近咩爪哇地區<br />\n以前聽得多果度成日地震<br />\n火山大爆發好似話有咩能量可以偵測"},{"pid":"4d4fb86f17158511af5a536f919045f67ca85819","tid":481468,"uid":18692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T17:51:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9a20fd9ea1f401d9f8a777de349f122671ef6c2","tid":481468,"uid":36901,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T18:08:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/3zqdmy6jqGs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F3zqdmy6jqGs&d=RF7omOGQ%2B7%2FbDvLEXCBJ7leK4D04he4k8uKHxpzC8zE%3D&h=bec33dac\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/3zqdmy6jqGs</a><br />\n<br />\nlive<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"865e7f28c718d71d57ce41db31b109a228fb2898","tid":481468,"uid":146243,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T18:19:23.000Z","msg":"<bl